PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774372288
OL,3,CDrug dealer found guilty of murder
OL,4,Cafter stamping on woman following car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FA drug dealer who stamped on a 56-year-
OL,8,Fold woman in a random attack in
OL,9,FLeicester has been found guilty of her
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FChukwuemeka Ahanonu, 23, was a
OL,13,Fstranger to mother Nila Patel, who
OL,14,Fdied in hospital two days after he
OL,15,Fattacked her, leaving her with brain
OL,16,Fdamage.
OL,18,FThe fatal attack happened after
OL,19,FAhanonu crashed and overturned the BMW
OL,20,Fhe was driving, near to the Leicester
OL,21,FRoyal Infirmary on 24 June 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774372288
OL,3,CDrug dealer found guilty of murder
OL,4,Cafter stamping on woman following car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FMs Patel had just got off a bus and
OL,8,Fwas talking on her phone to a friend
OL,9,Fas she walked along the road.
OL,11,FThe trial at Leicester Crown Court,
OL,12,Fheard that Ahanonu, of Dover Street,
OL,13,FLeicester, punched Ms Patel in the
OL,14,Fface with such severity that she fell
OL,15,Fonto the pavement. She was then kicked
OL,16,Fand stamped on as she lay on the floor.
OL,18,FAhanonu is due to be sentenced on
OL,19,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774372288
OL,3,CDrug dealer found guilty of murder
OL,4,Cafter stamping on woman following car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FEarlier in the trial, the jury was
OL,8,Ftold former university student Ahanonu
OL,9,Fwas freed from a two-year sentence in
OL,10,FJuly 2024, having been found with more
OL,11,Fthan #1,000 in cash and a machete
OL,12,Fafter going through a red light in
OL,13,FSeptember 2023.
OL,15,FProsecutors said that on the day of
OL,16,Fthe 'vicious attack', a blood test for
OL,17,Fcannabis showed Ahanonu was almost
OL,18,Ffour times the legal limit for driving.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774372288
OL,3,CDrug dealer found guilty of murder
OL,4,Cafter stamping on woman following car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FNo alcohol was found in a blood sample
OL,8,Ftaken around three hours after the
OL,9,Fmurder, but a test for THC, which is
OL,10,Fproduced by cannabis use, found a
OL,11,Flevel of 7.6mcg, above the limit of
OL,12,F2mcg.
OL,14,FProsecutor Mary Prior KC had told
OL,15,Fjurors that Ms Patel, who was 5ft 4in
OL,16,Ftall, was "viciously attacked" by
OL,17,FAhanonu, who was claiming universal
OL,18,Fcredit despite running a "significant"
OL,19,Fdrugs business.
OL,26,@xD@KOUxD@^O]zD@ZOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774372288
OL,3,CDrug dealer found guilty of murder
OL,4,Cafter stamping on woman following car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,FAlleging that the defendant had acted
OL,8,Fas he did because he had taken a lot
OL,9,Fof cannabis, Ms Prior told the jury:
OL,10,F"The voluntary consumption of a
OL,11,Fsubstance which causes you to act in a
OL,12,Fway that you would not act when sober
OL,13,Fis not a defence to murder because an
OL,14,Fintoxicated intent is still an intent."
OL,16,FMs Prior had told the trial: "She (Ms
OL,17,FPatel) had just got off the bus on her
OL,18,Fway home and was walking along the
OL,19,Froad, talking on the telephone to her
OL,20,Fdear friend.
OL,26,@rD@AOUvD@gO]xD@^OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774372288
OL,3,CDrug dealer found guilty of murder
OL,4,Cafter stamping on woman following car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"She was pulled from behind by the
OL,8,Fdefendant, punched in the face with
OL,9,Fsuch severity that she fell onto the
OL,10,Fpavement. She was then kicked and
OL,11,Fstamped on as she lay on the floor...
OL,12,Fstamped on her face."
OL,14,FDetective Inspector Emma Matts, of
OL,15,FLeicestershire Police, said: "Ahanonu
OL,16,Fwas unknown to Ms Patel. After
OL,17,Fcrashing his vehicle, he ran from the
OL,18,Fscene violently attacking Ms Patel.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@UO]wD@^OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774372288
OL,3,CDrug dealer found guilty of murder
OL,4,Cafter stamping on woman following car
OL,5,Ccrash
OL,7,F"This was the most horrific, violent
OL,8,Fand random attack by a stranger on a
OL,9,Fkind, gentle and loving woman who was
OL,10,Fsimply making her way home.
OL,12,F"It is hard to imagine what Ms Patel
OL,13,Fwent through in those moments. My
OL,14,Fthoughts continue to remain with her
OL,15,Fand with her family and friends who
OL,16,Fhave suffered and continue to suffer
OL,17,Fthe most horrendous distress and pain."
OL,19,FThe defendant is due to be sentenced
OL,20,Fon Tuesday.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@gO]
